I think we got the debuffs because they didn't know who else to give them to, other than an int caster, and somebody probably flipped a coin between magicians and wizards. Necros and enchanters already had debuff spells of their own. Wizards didn't get Lure's until the Kunark era and they got snares in Kunark too. So it wasn't an early design decision that gave us the malise line in exchange for giving wizards Lure spells. They didn't exist in the original release. <p>Artulyn Starsummoner Arch Mage<br>
